OL,3,CFerry workers to vote on strikes over
OL,4,Cjobs
OL,6,FFerry workers are to be balloted for
OL,7,Fstrikes in a dispute over jobs.
OL,9,FMembers of the Rail, Maritime and
OL,10,FTransport union (RMT) at ferry
OL,11,Foperator Wightlink will vote in the
OL,12,Fcoming weeks on whether to take
OL,13,Findustrial action.
OL,15,FThe union said efficiency plans
OL,16,Fthreatened 160 job losses.
