OL,3,CFerry workers to vote on strikes over
OL,4,Cjobs
OL,6,FRMT general secretary Eddie Dempsey
OL,7,Fsaid: "Cutting safety-critical roles
OL,8,Fand crewing ferries at bare minimum
OL,9,Flevels in one of the busiest stretches
OL,10,Fof water is a terrible idea for
OL,11,Fpassengers and for RMT members alike.
OL,13,F"Wightlink workers have given years of
OL,14,Fservice keeping the Solent moving and
OL,15,Fdeserve better than threats to their
OL,16,Fjobs and conditions.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
