OL,3,CFerry workers to vote on strikes over
OL,4,Cjobs
OL,6,F"Our proposals are essential for the
OL,7,Ffuture sustainability of Wightlink, to
OL,8,Fimprove flexibility and efficiency
OL,9,Fwhilst not reducing any services or
OL,10,Finvestment in our ports and fleet.
OL,11,FWhile legally we had to inform 160
OL,12,Fcolleagues that their roles were at
OL,13,Frisk, there are only 50 positions that
OL,14,Fmay go and alongside this there are
OL,15,Fover 30 new vacancies in the proposed
OL,16,Fnew structure.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
