OL,4,Cjobs
OL,6,F"We are doing everything we can to
OL,7,Favoid disruption and strike action as
OL,8,Fwe know the negative impact this has
OL,9,Fon our customers who rely on our
OL,10,Fservices. We continue to work with the
OL,11,FRMT to find a reasonable solution
OL,12,Fwhile future proofing the business to
OL,13,Fserve our island and mainland
OL,14,Fcustomers now and in the future."
